<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="134" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="134">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="134">
Besides the locations found by L. Pavesi for this species, published records include that of 
<bibRefCitation pageId="1" pageNumber="134">Ruffo (1960)</bibRefCitation>
in Sardinia and 
<bibRefCitation author="Ruffo, S" editor="Bellan-Santini, D" journalOrPublisher="Monaco" pageId="8" pageNumber="141" pagination="365 - 814" title="Memoires de l'Institut oceanographique." year="1993">Ruffo (1993)</bibRefCitation>
in France, Greece and Italy. Possibly some of these records refer to the species described below.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
